  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Packaged under ProfileMinimal; intended-use scope is not declared in this record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-worst-case-hemolysis",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-centrifugal-blood-pump-cfd",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-cbp-experimental-hemolysis-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/morrison-mesh-convergence-study"
  ],
