    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable under the ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 framework. The model is accepted for the decision question of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. No context of use object is bound in this minimal-profile package; use scope is defined externally by the submitting organisation.",
